MAPPING.DESCRIPTION: --as part of ITPR017177 Rebates Copy/Void Rewrite, added new targets, relation target for retained claims and flat file target for validation purpose. --ITPR017177 Rebates Copy/Void Rewrite we have made changes to existing mapping to load only new claims/changed claims to extn_clm_stg table and filter all retained claims and collect retained claims in the new relation target.
MAPPING.NAME: m_CASH_Load_RCNT_RECN_EXTN_CLM_STG

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: This lookup in conjunction with the parameter APC_STAT_CD (from TDISCNT_PERIOD) is used to determine if the INV_ID/HVST_ID is pre-APC/post-APC. There is a SQL override in the lookup, which has all model Harvest IDs in it.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_SNAP_APC_STAT_CD

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT MAX(SNP.SNAP_APC_TYP_CD) AS SNAP_APC_STAT_CD, DTL.HVST_ID as HVST_ID, DTL.INV_ID as INV_ID FROM VRAP.TSNAP_INV_DTL DTL, VRAP.TSNAP SNP, VRAP.RCNT_RECN_PARAM PRM WHERE DTL.HVST_ID = PRM.HVST_ID AND DTL.SNAP_ID = SNP.SNAP_ID AND SNP.SNAP_SEQ_NB > 0 GROUP BY DTL.HVST_ID, DTL.INV_ID WITH UR; --SQL Override

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: This lookup Pulls APC_STAT_CD data based on PERIOD_ID passed.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: lkp_get_APC_STAT_CD

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT DISTINCT PRM.APC_STAT_CD as APC_STAT_CD, PRM.PERIOD_ID as PERIOD_ID FROM VRAP.RCNT_RECN_PARAM PRM WITH UR; -- SQL Override

TRANSFORMFIELD.DESCRIPTION: A system generated unique identifier for each data harvest process, using seque
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: HVST_ID

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT QUE.SEG_CD as SEG_CD, QUE.HVST_ID as HVST_ID FROM VRAP.THARVEST_QUE QUE, VRAP.RCNT_RECN_PARAM PRM WHERE QUE.HVST_ID= PRM.HVST_ID WITH UR; -- SQL Override

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: This lookup pulls discount tier drug related info (like admin, base rate) from all the model specific tables.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_VTDISCNT_RPT_DRUG_TIER_ALLMODELS

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Expression for REBT_TYP_CD - IF MKSR_RPT_ID is null, then 0. else 1. Expression for evaluating FILL_PRD_MTH_ID. Expression for evaluating FILL_PRD_QTR_ID. Expressions for evaluating APC Amount fields.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: EXP_MISC

TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: FILL_PRD_MTH_ID
FILL_PRD_QTR_ID

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION:
iif(APC_STAT_CD='O', false, iif(in(SNAP_APC_STAT_CD,1,2,3,4), false, true) )
-- Negative logic required because the loader may not have run by the time APC has kicked off.
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: v_Post_APC_flag

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION:
iif(v_Post_APC_flag, 0, ADMN_DISCNT_AMT_in )
-- if post-APC, the 0, else ADMN_DISCNT_AMT
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: ADMN_DISCNT_APC_AMT_out

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION:
iif(v_Post_APC_flag, 0, BASE_DISCNT_AMT_in )
-- if post-APC, the 0, else BASE_DISCNT_AMT
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: BASE_DISCNT_APC_AMT_out

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION:
iif(v_Post_APC_flag, 0, CNTRCT_DISCNT_AMT_in )
-- if post-APC, the 0, else CNTRCT_DISCNT_AMT
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: CNTRCT_DISCNT_APC_AMT

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION:
iif(v_Post_APC_flag, 0, FRMLY_DISCNT_AMT_in )
-- if post-APC, the 0, else FRMLY_DISCNT_AMT
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: FRMLY_DISCNT_APC_AMT_out

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION:
iif(v_Post_APC_flag, 0, PRFMC_DISCNT_AMT_in )
-- if post-APC, the 0, else PRFMC_DISCNT_AMT
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: PRFMC_DISCNT_APC_AMT_out

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION:
iif(v_Post_APC_flag, 0, PRC_PTCT_DISCNT_AMT_in )
-- if post-APC, the 0, else PRC_PTCT_DISCNT_AMT
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: PRC_PTCT_DISCNT_APC_AMT_in

GROUP.DESCRIPTION: Path for the data when none of the group conditions are satisfied.
GROUP.NAME: DEFAULT1

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: This lookup pulls drug related info (like admin, base rate) from all the model specific tables.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_VTRPT_DRUG_FLAT_BASIS_ALLMODELS

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: HVST_ID = HVST_ID_In AND DRUG_NDC_ID = NDC_ID_In AND NHU_TYP_CD = NHU_TYP_CD_In

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: looking up on RCNT_RECN_EXTN_CLM to check if its a new/changed claim or retained claim.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_RCNT_RECN_EXTN_CLM

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT DISTINCT --CLM.CLM_GID AS CLM_GID, -- Removed since if HVST is available, which means all claims in the HVST should be available. CLM.RPT_ID AS RPT_ID, CLM.INV_ID AS INV_ID, CLM.RECN_GID AS RECN_GID, CLM.HVST_ID AS HVST_ID FROM VRAP.RCNT_RECN_EXTN_CLM CLM, VRAP.RCNT_RECN_PARAM PRM WHERE CLM.HVST_ID=PRM.HVST_ID AND CLM.RECN_GID = PRM.RECN_GID AND CLM.RECN_SCRB_CD <> $$PARM_SCRB_CD WITH UR; --LKP SQL Override

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT HDR.DSTR_GID as DSTR_GID, HDR.RECN_GID as RECN_GID FROM VRAP.RCNT_RECN_DSTR_HDR HDR, (SELECT DISTINCT RECN_GID FROM VRAP.RCNT_RECN_PARAM) PRM WHERE HDR.DSTR_STAT_CD = $$PARM_RECN_DSTR_TYP_DUMMY AND HDR.RECN_GID = PRM.RECN_GID WITH UR; -- SQL Override

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Pulls all model information from below claims main tables VRAP.TDISCNT_EXT_CLAIM_*, (That is from All Model Specific Tables) VRAP.RCIT_CLM_INV_ELIG and RECON_GID and INV_ID from header tables.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: SQ_VDISCNT_EXT_CLAIM_ALLMODELS

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT CLM_ALL_MODELS.CLAIM_ID, CLM_ALL_MODELS.EXTNL_SRC_CD, CLM_ALL_MODELS.RPT_ID, CLM_ALL_MODELS.PERIOD_ID, CLM_ALL_MODELS.DISCNT_RUN_MODE_CD, CLM_ALL_MODELS.MKSR_RPT_ID, CLM_ALL_MODELS.ADMN_DISCNT_FCTR, CLM_ALL_MODELS.BASE_DISCNT_FCTR, CLM_ALL_MODELS.PRFMC_DISCNT_FCTR, CLM_ALL_MODELS.FRMLY_DISCNT_FCTR, CLM_ALL_MODELS.PRC_PTCT_DISCNT_FCTR, CLM_ALL_MODELS.ADMN_DRUG_PRC_AMT, CLM_ALL_MODELS.BASE_DRUG_PRC_AMT, CLM_ALL_MODELS.PRFMC_DRUG_PRC_AMT, CLM_ALL_MODELS.FRMLY_DRUG_PRC_AMT, CLM_ALL_MODELS.CNTRCT_DRUG_PRC_AMT, CLM_ALL_MODELS.CNTRCT_PRC_AMT, CLM_ALL_MODELS.ADMN_DISCNT_AMT, CLM_ALL_MODELS.BASE_DISCNT_AMT, CLM_ALL_MODELS.PRFMC_DISCNT_AMT, CLM_ALL_MODELS.FRMLY_DISCNT_AMT, CLM_ALL_MODELS.CNTRCT_DISCNT_AMT, CLM_ALL_MODELS.PRC_PTCT_DISCNT_AMT, CLM_ALL_MODELS.HVST_ID, CLM_ALL_MODELS.AP_CO_CD, CLM_ALL_MODELS.RPT_AP_CO_CD, CLM_ALL_MODELS.DSPN_DT, CLM_ALL_MODELS.NABP_ID, CLM_ALL_MODELS.NDC_ID, CLM_ALL_MODELS.LCM_CD, CLM_ALL_MODELS.CLM_TYP_CD, CLM_ALL_MODELS.DY_SPLY_QTY, CLM_ALL_MODELS.UQ_QTY, CLM_ALL_MODELS.INV_ELIG_DT, CLM_ALL_MODELS.NHU_TYP_CD, CLM_ALL_MODELS.DLVY_SYS_CD, CLM_ALL_MODELS.FRMLY_SRC_CD, CLM_ALL_MODELS.INCTV_TYP_CD, CLM_ALL_MODELS.PMCY_NPI_ID, CLM_ALL_MODELS.RBAT_ID, CLM_ALL_MODELS.NEW_REFIL_CD, CLM_ALL_MODELS.RX_NB, CLM_ALL_MODELS.FRMLY_ID, CLM_ALL_MODELS.BNSTG_BEG_CD, CLM_ALL_MODELS.BNSTG_END_CD, CLM_ALL_MODELS.ADJD_BRND_GNRC_CD, CLM_ALL_MODELS.GPDSC_APLD_CD, CLM_ALL_MODELS.CLM_GAP_PCT, CLM_ALL_MODELS.FRMLY_DRUG_STAT_CD, CLM_ALL_MODELS.CLT_ID, CLM_ALL_MODELS.BUS_SEG_CD, HDR.RECN_GID, HDR.VEND_ID, HDR.CO_BE_ID, MHDR.INV_ID, DTL.MODEL_TYP_CD FROM VRAP.VDISCNT_EXT_CLAIM_ALLMODELS CLM_ALL_MODELS, VRAP.RCNT_RBAT_MFG_INV_HDR MHDR, VRAP.RCNT_RBAT_MFG_INV_DTL DTL, VRAP.RCNT_RECN_HDR HDR, VRAP.RCNT_RECN_PARAM PRM WHERE CLM_ALL_MODELS.HVST_ID=DTL.HVST_ID AND CLM_ALL_MODELS.RPT_ID=DTL.RPT_ID AND DTL.INV_ID = MHDR.INV_ID AND HDR.RECN_GID = MHDR.RECN_GID AND DTL.HVST_ID = PRM.HVST_ID AND MHDR.RECN_GID = PRM.RECN_GID AND MHDR.INV_ID= PRM.INV_ID AND MHDR.INV_STAT_CD = 1 WITH UR; --SQL Override
